- Replace variable working-days-based monthly goal with flat 125 hrs/mo
- Replace variable available time with flat 157 hrs/mo (1880 ÷ 12)
- Matches 2026 Firm Dashboard assumptions (47 weeks × 8hrs × 5 days = 1880)
- Updated both generate_weekly_goals (JSON) and downloadWeeklyGoals (Excel)
- Removed unused dailyGoal variable
---
 src/tools/documents.ts | 13 +++++++++----
 src/tools/scorecard.ts | 20 +++++++++++---------
 2 files changed, 20 insertions(+), 13 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/tools/documents.ts b/src/tools/documents.ts
